                            <comment id="17153540" author="gwlucas" created="Wed, 8 Jul 2020 12:07:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I might be able to take a look at this.  Does anyone have sample images?   In particular, it would require something relatively small that could be added to the test images, but which unambiguously demonstrates the problem (both for coding and for visual inspection when it&apos;s done).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17221429" author="gwlucas" created="Tue, 27 Oct 2020 13:25:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am finishing up work on this fix and will be submitting a code update in the near future.&#160; &#160;There are some sample images now available in the test data space for TIFF files.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17233262" author="kinow" created="Tue, 17 Nov 2020 05:17:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=gwlucas&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;gwlucas&quot;&gt;gwlucas&lt;/a&gt; &apos; pull request. Thanks Gary!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
